OL,3,CLabour MP calls for more changes to
OL,4,CHillsborough Law to get rid of
OL,5,C'loopholes'
OL,7,FA Labour MP has called for further
OL,8,Fchanges to the proposed Hillsborough
OL,9,FLaw amid concerns that it leaves
OL,10,Floopholes in applying the duty of
OL,11,Fcandour to the intelligence services.
OL,13,FAmendments proposed by the Government
OL,14,Fon Wednesday 14 January brought spies
OL,15,Fwithin the scope of the legislation,
OL,16,Fsubject to the approval of the head of
OL,17,Ftheir service.
