OL,3,CLabour MP calls for more changes to
OL,4,CHillsborough Law to get rid of
OL,5,C'loopholes'
OL,7,FBut campaigners have said this would
OL,8,Fallow the heads of the security
OL,9,Fservices to decide whether to disclose
OL,10,Finformation.
OL,12,FLiverpool West Derby MP Ian Byrne
OL,13,Fposted on social media platform X: "I
OL,14,Fcannot, in all good conscience,
OL,15,Fsupport any amendments that abandon
OL,16,Fthe Manchester Arena bombing families,
OL,17,Fnuclear test veterans, or the Chinook
OL,18,Fdisaster families.
OL,26,@uD@dOU
