OL,3,CLabour MP calls for more changes to
OL,4,CHillsborough Law to get rid of
OL,5,C'loopholes'
OL,7,F"I made a commitment to deliver the
OL,8,FHillsborough Law... without
OL,9,Fexemptions, without loopholes and
OL,10,Fwithout carve-outs.
OL,12,F"The Government made this promise in
OL,13,Fits manifesto. If the Government's
OL,14,Famendments are passed then the
OL,15,Flegislation, in its current form, is
OL,16,Fnot that."
