OL,3,CLabour MP calls for more changes to
OL,4,CHillsborough Law to get rid of
OL,5,C'loopholes'
OL,7,FMr Byrne has tabled several amendments
OL,8,Fof his own so the duty of candour
OL,9,Fwould apply not only to intelligence
OL,10,Forganisations but also to people who
OL,11,Fwork for them.
OL,13,FHe urged Sir Keir Starmer to drop his
OL,14,Famendments and deliver a version that
OL,15,Fis not "watered down".
OL,17,FFailing that, he urged MPs to reject
OL,18,Fthe Government's amendments and
OL,19,Fsupport his instead.
OL,26,@wD@HOUwD@UO]
