OL,3,CLabour MP calls for more changes to
OL,4,CHillsborough Law to get rid of
OL,5,C'loopholes'
OL,7,FKim Johnson, Liverpool Riverside MP,
OL,8,Fagreed with her parliamentary
OL,9,Fcolleague, posting on X: "This is not
OL,10,Fthe Bill we were promised by the Prime
OL,11,FMinister. We need a full duty of
OL,12,Fcandour for every public body.
OL,14,F"If it doesn't apply to all, it's not
OL,15,Fthe Hillsborough Law and doesn't
OL,16,Fdeserve the name."
OL,26,@qD@ZOUvD@AOUxD@RO]
