OL,3,CLabour MP calls for more changes to
OL,4,CHillsborough Law to get rid of
OL,5,C'loopholes'
OL,7,FBut campaigners have been left
OL,8,Fdisappointed.
OL,10,FElkan Abrahamson, a lawyer for the
OL,11,FHillsborough Law Now campaign, said
OL,12,Fthe amendments allowed the heads of
OL,13,Fthe security services to make
OL,14,F"whatever decision they want" on
OL,15,Fwhether to disclose information and
OL,16,Fleft them "unchallengeable".
OL,26,@vD@AOUvD@]O]xD@KOUxD@[O]
