OL,3,CLabour MP calls for more changes to
OL,4,CHillsborough Law to get rid of
OL,5,C'loopholes'
OL,7,FHe said it should be up to the head of
OL,8,Fan inquiry to decide whether
OL,9,Finformation was relevant, adding there
OL,10,Fwere already national security
OL,11,Fexemptions that allowed evidence to be
OL,12,Fheard in private.
OL,14,FRuth Leney, who chairs the Manchester
OL,15,FArena Support Network, said: "We can't
OL,16,Ftrust the Bill if not everybody is
OL,17,Faccountable to it."
OL,26,@wD@^OUyD@SO]
