OL,3,CLabour MP calls for more changes to
OL,4,CHillsborough Law to get rid of
OL,5,C'loopholes'
OL,7,FA Government spokesperson said: "We
OL,8,Fare bringing in a landmark piece of
OL,9,Flegislation putting a legal duty on
OL,10,Fofficials to respond openly and
OL,11,Fhonestly when things go wrong.
OL,13,F"This would not have been possible
OL,14,Fwithout the tireless campaigning from
OL,15,Fvictims and families who have lost
OL,16,Floved ones and we are determined to
OL,17,Fmake this Bill a lasting legacy to the
OL,18,Fdecades they have called for change.
OL,26,@oD@aOUuD@AOU
