OL,7,F"We have listened to their concerns on
OL,8,Fhow the duty of candour will apply to
OL,9,Fthe security services and we will
OL,10,Fcontinue to work with them to make the
OL,11,FBill as strong as it can possibly be,
OL,12,Fwhile never compromising on national
OL,13,Fsecurity."
